text:
Flushing Meadow Park: (Worlds Fair Grounds). Three views showing the Tower completed and the Sphere under construction. View No. 1 shows the Grand Central Parkway in the foreground and the entrance to the Fair by the Long Island Railroad. Beyond it, in midground of the view are the Administration Buildings. View No. 2 look north east from 111th Street and Fifty-sixth Avenue. View No. 3 shows the sphere practically completed.

May 30, 1938.
Views 1 and 2
View 3: July 3, 1938.

P.L. Sperr

View # 3: 4908
title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - Alpine Avenue
